---
Source:
  - Title: Rainbows Appear
    Editor: Matthieu Ricard
    ISBN: 9781570629822
By: Shabkar
---
Your prime goal
 must always be
To generate and nurture
 in your heart a love
That is such that the pain of others
 is unberable to you.
Carry on like this until the birth
Of true compassion,
 natural and spontaneous.
